Your program should work as follows:</p>
<div class="language-console highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="gp">example@example:~$</span><span class="w"> </span>./addition
<span class="go">1st number: 2
2nd number: 4
6
</span></code></pre></div></div>

